       p. 94. $)
    ntrval $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ S C_ X ) -> ( ( int ` J ) ` S ) =
                 U. ( J i^i ~P S ) ) $=
      ( vx ctop wcel wss wa cnt cfv cpw cv cin cuni cmpt wceq adantr cvv syl wb
