      ZVLUPVMUQBVHFUFRVISUGTEAVEVJVASVFVBAQZVDVIVNVCVHBVBAUHUIUJVFUKULUNUO $.
      $( [11-Nov-2013] $) $( [10-Sep-2006] $)

    $( The closure of a subset of a topology's base set is the intersection of
